title: Lily Ramsay
text: Hi, and welcome to my corner of the internet. I’m a data analyst with over 8 years of experience, currently working for the US government in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. This website serves as my resume and a hub for projects, notes, and other odds and ends. Whether you’re here to explore my work, collaborate, or simply connect, I’m excited to share this part of my world with you.

title: About Me
text: Hi, I’m Lily. I grew up in central Texas and have lived in Vermont, Italy, Tennessee, and now Philadelphia. I have a degree in History and still enjoy the occasional historical work, currently diving into Empire of Wealth. I’m a lifelong fan of the San Antonio Spurs and am learning to enjoy the Birds. I also love spending time outdoors, having hiked several of the major US trails, and even climbed Mount Kilimanjaro last year. In my downtime, I enjoy playing video games, from immersive series like The Witcher to cozy games like Stardew Valley. I’m a curious person, seeking answers for questions through experiences with new places, books, outdoor adventures, or games.
